{"id":"api/core/defer","title":"@defer","contents":"<article>\n  <div class=\"breadcrumb-container\">\n    <div class=\"breadcrumb\">\n      <script type=\"application/ld+json\">\n        {\n          \"@context\": \"http://schema.org\",\n          \"@type\": \"BreadcrumbList\",\n          \"itemListElement\": [\n            { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 1, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.io/api\", \"name\": \"API\" } },\n            { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 2, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.io/api/core\", \"name\": \"@angular/core\" } },\n            { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 3, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.io/api/core/defer\", \"name\": \"@defer\" } }\n          ]\n        }\n      </script>\n        <a href=\"/api\">API</a> &gt; <a href=\"api/core\">@angular/core</a>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"github-links\">\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/ng-docs/angular-cn/tree/17.3.0-next.1/aio/content/blocks/core/defer.md\" aria-label=\"檢視原始碼\" title=\"檢視原始碼\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">code</i></a>\n</div>\n  </div>\n  <header class=\"api-header\">\n    <h1 id=\"defer\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"25d5jzaq3sa7wmrmg5tm2mq7n\">@defer<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/core/defer#defer\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h1>\n    <label class=\"api-type-label block\">block</label>\n  </header>\n  \n\n  <div class=\"api-body\">\n  <section class=\"short-description\">\n    <p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"en02iqv7cff0w0dads5qzruam\">一種\n<a href=\"api/core/defer\">區塊</a>型別，可用於延遲載入元件、指令和通道在元件樣板中使用的JavaScript。</p>\n\n    <p><a href=\"api/core/defer#description\">檢視更多...</a></p>\n  </section>\n  \n    <h2 id=\"syntax\">語法<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/core/defer#syntax\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n    <code-example language=\"html\">\n@defer ( on &lt;<a href=\"api/animations/trigger\" class=\"code-anchor\">trigger</a>&gt;; when &lt;condition&gt;; prefetch on &lt;<a href=\"api/animations/trigger\" class=\"code-anchor\">trigger</a>&gt;; prefetch when &lt;condition&gt; ) {\n  &lt;!-- deferred template fragment --&gt;\n  &lt;calendar-cmp /&gt;\n} @placeholder ( minimum? &lt;duration&gt; ) {\n  &lt;!-- placeholder template fragment --&gt;\n  &lt;p&gt;Placeholder&lt;/p&gt;\n} @loading ( minimum? &lt;duration&gt;; after? &lt;duration&gt; ) {\n  &lt;!-- loading template fragment --&gt;\n  &lt;<a href=\"api/common/NgOptimizedImage\" class=\"code-anchor\">img</a> alt=\"loading image\" src=\"loading.gif\" /&gt;\n} @error {\n  &lt;!-- error template fragment --&gt;\n  &lt;p&gt;An loading error occurred&lt;/p&gt;\n}\n</code-example>\n\n  \n\n  \n<section class=\"description\">\n  <h2 id=\"description\">說明<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/core/defer#description\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n  <h3 id=\"blocks\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"a5xwaqbi0e61umqg5kpxpysa\">區塊<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/core/defer#blocks\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h3>\n<p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"4kphcgik15eyqtzty3zb6ou56\">延遲載入區塊的支援部分。注意：僅@defer區塊樣板片段是延遲載入的。其餘的可選區塊是急性載入的。</p>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>block</th>\n<th data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"ar5q09mdsagdppsbze96eagxl\">說明</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td><code><a href=\"api/core/defer\" class=\"code-anchor\">@defer</a></code></td>\n<td data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"7ncdykqvxmui9lthmnzkzkvha\">延遲載入的內容區塊</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><code>@placeholder</code></td>\n<td data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"5xafrdqxrdjav9cebsv6hbc1t\">延遲載入之前顯示的內容（可選）</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><code>@loading</code></td>\n<td data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"4vlykd9modrk3p8sc0a6hrwb8\">延遲載入期間顯示的內容（可選）</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><code>@error</code></td>\n<td data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"6nv3souilty4zrn78uppsvv08\">延遲載入發生錯誤時顯示的內容（可選）</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<h3 id=\"triggers\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"7vgcf722ylvmkj1nb28q7j5wh\">觸發器<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/core/defer#triggers\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h3>\n<p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"d4078tzd6994utsabo2omhmcr\">觸發器提供了延遲載入發生的條件。某些允許樣板引用變數作為可選引數。使用分號分隔多個觸發器。</p>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>trigger</th>\n<th data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"chrftc36h0dra0jgjcecpi2r5\">觸發器...</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td><code>on idle</code></td>\n<td data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"53x6wpl3jqd6wiewxsngsmnut\">當瀏覽器報告空閒狀態時（預設）</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><code>on viewport(&lt;elementRef&gt;?)</code></td>\n<td data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"baz9r7qizgyn8zn2k0nbi9715\">當元素進入視口時</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><code>on interaction(&lt;elementRef&gt;?)</code></td>\n<td data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"f37a8qfrr4r3ewivrlck9if2q\">當點選、觸控或聚焦時</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><code>on hover(&lt;elementRef&gt;?)</code></td>\n<td data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"9kvfnil1dgpoub07wzaq496le\">當元素被懸停時</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><code>on immediate</code></td>\n<td data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"eausq0hfjn34pjomy76ivhjhz\">當頁面完成渲染後</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><code>on timer(&lt;duration&gt;)</code></td>\n<td data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"f4fe7homtdj5wbykva9lab3hf\">在特定超時後</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><code>when &lt;condition&gt;</code></td>\n<td data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"1nggkx2xdfznn3imve6x4yxjh\">在自定義條件上</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<h2 id=\"prefetch\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"1fumgg87uab6lcwe4e1hafk3y\">預取<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/core/defer#prefetch\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n<p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"2zvs28tq3iz5ms51cgv8scut4\">設定延遲塊中使用的預取，但不影響渲染。渲染由標準的 \n<code>on</code> 和 \n<code>when</code> 條件處理。用分號分隔多個預取設定。</p>\n<code-example language=\"html\">\n@defer (prefetch on &lt;<a href=\"api/animations/trigger\" class=\"code-anchor\">trigger</a>&gt;; prefetch when &lt;condition&gt;) {\n  &lt;!-- deferred template fragment --&gt;\n}\n</code-example>\n<p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"azw45pjb9kmfio5ql9fe1spna\">在 \n<a href=\"guide/defer\">延遲載入指南</a> 中瞭解更多訊息。</p>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article>\n\n<!-- links to this doc:\n - guide/defer\n-->\n<!-- links from this doc:\n - /api\n - api/animations/trigger\n - api/common/NgOptimizedImage\n - api/core\n - api/core/defer#blocks\n - api/core/defer#defer\n - api/core/defer#description\n - api/core/defer#prefetch\n - api/core/defer#syntax\n - api/core/defer#triggers\n - guide/defer\n - https://github.com/ng-docs/angular-cn/tree/17.3.0-next.1/aio/content/blocks/core/defer.md\n-->"}